for a little Joy time.

03:38.319 --> 03:41.955
** [ Muttering ]

03:42.022 --> 03:44.124
What Montel failed to mention...

03:44.191 --> 03:47.828
is that when your wife
is four margaritas deep
into her alone time--

03:47.895 --> 03:49.830
* Check baby, check baby
One, two, three, four *

03:49.897 --> 03:53.066
* Check baby, check baby
One, two, three *

03:53.133 --> 03:56.304
all that fightin' she's
been doin' with her husband...

03:56.370 --> 03:58.739
