into the arms of another man.

03:58.806 --> 04:01.942
And just like that,
Joy found the solution
to her marital problems--

04:02.009 --> 04:04.177
adultery.

04:04.244 --> 04:07.681
And over the next few months,
Joy and Darnell
started to get real close.

04:07.748 --> 04:09.983
[ Earl ]
Hello! Happy Thanksgiving!

04:10.050 --> 04:11.852
[ Whispering ]
Get in the closet.

04:14.254 --> 04:16.324
What are you doin' in bed?

04:16.390 --> 04:20.628
Waitin' for you to get home
to give me my Thanksgiving
stuffing.

04:20.694 --> 04:23.964
Really? All right.
It's been a while.

04:24.031 --> 04:26.900
I'll try not to touch you
too much. My hands are cold.

04:26.967 --> 04:28.802
They smell like turkey.

04:32.139 --> 04:35.108
[ Earl Narrating ]
Of course, now I kick myself
for not seein' the signs,

04:35.175 --> 04:39.613
but sometimes
the truth is hardest to see
when it's right in front of you.

04:39.680 --> 04:42.383
Whoa, check out
this long black hair.

04:43.951 --> 04:47.655
Man, I wish I would've seen this
when it was still on me.

04:47.721 --> 04:49.923
[ Earl Narrating ]
Joy and Darnell
were fallin' in love.

04:49.990 --> 04:52.760
But no matter how much
two people love each other,

04:52.826 --> 04:55.496
the stresses of adultery can put
strain on any relationship.

04:55.563 --> 04:58.231
I don't like having sex
in the walk-in freezer.

04:58.298 --> 05:00.300
It's cold in there,
but we still get sweaty.

05:00.368 --> 05:03.604
Last time, my balls got stuck
to a keg of beer.
All right, fine.

05:03.671 --> 05:06.574
We'll wait till this place
closes, and you can do me
on the pinball machine...

05:06.640 --> 05:08.676
