05:20.754 --> 05:23.457
Excuse me. I didn't
realize I was screwin'
Encyclopedia Brown.

05:23.524 --> 05:26.193
[ Earl Narrating ]
What Darnell was about
to learn...

05:26.259 --> 05:29.262
