sent her running to him,

05:29.329 --> 05:32.700
and him and her arguin' was
gonna send her right back to me.

05:34.735 --> 05:36.770
Take me to bed
or lose me forever.

05:36.837 --> 05:39.573
Really? All right.
Been a while.

05:39.640 --> 05:44.545
I'll try not to touch you
too much. My hands are hot,
and they smell like poop.

05:44.612 --> 05:46.714
[ Earl Narrating ]
