08:23.470 --> 08:26.674
[ Earl Narrating ]
Before we knew it,
the big day was here.

08:26.740 --> 08:31.244
- [ Screaming ]
- [ Baby Crying ]

08:37.785 --> 08:40.821
Joy?
Yeah, sweetie?

08:40.888 --> 08:45.492
